	CONT.SYSMESSAGE As your stamina is full, the sword burns the stolen points.
ELSE
	CONT.SYSMESSAGE Your sword steals stamina from the enemy and give it to you!
	CONT.STAM=(<CONT.STAM>+5)	
ENDIF

